sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant GHA as GitHub Actions
    participant GHCR as GHCR (Container Registry)
    participant Prod as Production Host (Swarm Manager)
    participant LB as Traefik (Load Balancer)
    participant Web as Django web replicas
    participant Worker as Celery worker replicas

    Dev->>GH: git push to main
    GH->>GHA: Trigger deploy workflow

    GHA->>GHA: Run tests (pytest)
    alt Tests fail
        GHA-->>Dev: Notify failure — deploy aborted
    end

    GHA->>GHA: docker build (multi-stage: frontend + Django)
    GHA->>GHCR: docker push ghcr.io/org/app:<sha>

    GHA->>Prod: SSH — docker service update app_web --image <sha>
    Prod->>Web: Rolling update (one replica at a time)
    Web->>LB: Health check GET /health/ (200 OK required before traffic)
    LB-->>Web: Traffic restored once healthy

    GHA->>Prod: SSH — docker service update app_celery-worker --image <sha>
    Prod->>Worker: Rolling update

    GHA-->>Dev: Notify deploy complete

    note over Prod: Nightly PG backup (cron @ 02:00)
    Prod->>Prod: docker service update --force app_pg-backup
    Prod->>Prod: pg_dump | gzip | aws s3 cp → s3://backup-bucket/postgres/<timestamp>.sql.gz
